  "subject": "Changes to has-api to run on TLS/https. In order for the api to run in a robust and production-grade server (uwsgi over nginx) and to make container level certificate changes smart and easy, we have changed the image to have all thats required to run a uwsgi application. Earlier, the api component was running on http and in a single-threaded model.",
  "commit_message": "Changes to has-api to run on TLS/https. In order for the api to run in a robust and production-grade server (uwsgi over nginx) and to make container level certificate changes smart and easy, we have changed the image to have all thats required to run a uwsgi application. Earlier, the api component was running on http and in a single-threaded model.\n\nIssue-ID: OPTFRA-461\nChange-Id: I8f40017a1365a82c00456ffde2c69d8afd567534\nSigned-off-by: Ikramullah, Ikram <ikram@research.att.com>\n",
